<c74object name='fluid.audiofilesin' category='Fluid Corpus Manipulation'>
    <digest>Collect audio from a directory</digest>
    <description>A convenience abstraction for collecting all audio files in a directory into a list.</description>
    <discussion>
        <h4><openfilelink filename="Fluid Corpus Manipulation Toolkit.maxpat">Open the Overview Patch</openfilelink></h4>
        Given a valid path to a directory on disk, this abstraction reports all audio files that Max can open in that directory.

        <p>fluid.audiofilesin is part of the Fluid Decomposition Toolkit of the FluCoMa project. For more explanations, learning material, and discussions on its musicianly uses, visit <a href="http://www.flucoma.org/">flucoma.org</a>.</p>
